title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Norway Roads, Eastern Norway, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Norway Roads, Eastern Norway, 2008
description: This Dataset is part of three datasets downloaded from the openstreetmap, Geofabrik website and includes information and locations of roads throughout Eastern Norway. The dataset includes Road names and type. Type of road includes information on whether the road is a primary, residential or secondary road, etc. Because the dataset for the entire country was too big, it was divided into eastern, central and western Norway.
